            </p>

            <h3>✨ Key Features</h3>
            <ul class="weather-features">
              <li>Real-time weather data from OpenWeatherMap API</li>
              <li>5-day weather forecast with detailed metrics</li>
              <li>Interactive temperature and humidity trend charts</li>
              <li>Responsive dashboard with metric cards</li>
              <li>Dynamic city search functionality</li>
              <li>Data visualization with Matplotlib</li>
            </ul>

